ndex":179,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"68e4df1526"},{"id":"48e001c52d","type":"paragraph","text":"丙、不能亲人的供养、教育不管，使他受苦④。对国、对社会、对人类同一原理。","index":180,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"68e4df1526"},{"id":"facc3c18c6","type":"paragraph","text":"［注］","index":181,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"68e4df1526"},{"id":"a79c9e9deb","type":"paragraph","text":"①这一则也是林彪的亲笔。据原编者说明，写在1963年《工作手册》（十）上。小字经原“林办”工作人员辨认，是林立果的笔迹。","index":182,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"68e4df1526"},{"id":"f51ecc6961","type":"paragraph","text":"②朱理治，中国共产党建立初期加入的共产党员。他不赞成毛泽东的“五四”运动属于无产阶级领导的观点，认为“五四”是知识分子领导的。","index":183,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"68e4df1526"},{"id":"1e35665fc4","type":"paragraph","text":"③“彭”，指彭德怀。","index":184,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"68e4df1526"},{"id":"0dbb36966e","type":"paragraph","text":"④此处可能指林彪前妻张梅所生的小琳因叶群不喜欢而在外流浪，不能进京的事。","index":185,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"68e4df1526"},{"id":"902276c9d5","type":"subtitle","text":"其十四①","index":186,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"68e4df1526"},{"id":"75dc945808","type":"subtitle","text":"1962.01.23","index":187,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"68e4df1526"},{"id":"9d8b652720","type":"paragraph","text":"睡好觉，身体乃一切之物基。","index":188,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"68e4df1526"},{"id":"12e6122254","type":"paragraph","text":"一○一人大会堂五级干会报苦经教②：（1）秀才不行，束缚于既成思想词句或目空一切。","index":189,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"68e4df1526"},{"id":"94706adca6","type":"paragraph","text":"（2）不怕人多会大（反正有麦克风），只对一二人，对表情亲善者，以增信心。","index":190,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"68e4df1526"},{"id":"3f1646a363","type":"paragraph","text":"（3）另件箱法③有大效：一深刻，二可以应付任何急活。","index":191,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"68e4df1526"},{"id":"4a8f6619bb","type":"subtitle","text":"（4）另件逐一列出，再梳成几条辫子，而成一良好报告。","index":192,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"68e4df1526"},{"id":"6b4a4d6993","type":"paragraph","text":"（5）无论任何会，讲任何问题，都需要有典型例子，论点才能立体化，易解，生色——凡例皆大笑。","index":193,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"68e4df1526"},{"id":"b3be1ec169","type":"paragraph","text":"（6）每纸留小半页，用填例子，利用红笔。","index":194,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"68e4df1526"},{"id":"a427808366","type":"paragraph","text":"（7）原来次序，可于讲话时依自己情绪，听众及首长之不同反应而改换之（如插话、鼓掌、振动）。勿被原次序所束缚。用划勾法免漏。","index":195,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"68e4df1526"},{"id":"2162ecda27","type":"paragraph","text":"（8）初稿时应请内行阅，以免差误。","index":196,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"68e4df1526"},{"id":"0b8842b9b2","type":"paragraph","text":"（9）好辞藻、好知识、历史、好哲理、现代常识总有用，平时应大量积累。","index":197,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"68e4df1526"},{"id":"a97b3ecfd0","type":"paragraph","text":"（10）讲时应照顾听众利益，及大首脑（一号、干部辛苦、各脑、周）利益，分别拉之。","index":198,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"68e4df1526"},{"id":"517525a01d","type":"paragraph","text":"（11）长讲话：鼓动放前，先鼓动起劲，把精彩的放前，如电影，才能听下去。短：可放后，以有余味。","index":199,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"68e4df1526"},{"id":"7396851446","type":"paragraph","text":"［注］","index":200,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"68e4df1526"},{"id":"daa38c2c26","type":"paragraph","text":"①林彪为准备1962年1月29日在五级干部会《七千人大会》上讲话，谈了准备方法和注意要点，这是叶群作的记录。","index":201,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"68e4df1526"},{"id":"898962a097","type":"paragraph","text":"②“经教”，经验教训之省略语。","index":202,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"68e4df1526"},{"id":"c1b4b00769","type":"paragraph","text":"③“另件箱”，指分类储存的各种语录和材料。","index":203,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"68e4df1526"},{"id":"f95e4e19e6","type":"subtitle","text":"其十五①","index":204,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"68e4df1526"},{"id":"fe737941a5","type":"paragraph","text":"三级表态：说坏——右","index":205,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"68e4df1526"},{"id":"49cf27f23d","type":"paragraph","text":"不说——中","index":206,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"68e4df1526"},{"id":"f2bd44fabc","type":"paragraph","text":"说好——左","index":207,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"68e4df1526"},{"id":"ea60f1d4e3","type":"paragraph","text":"［注］","index":208,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","ar